--------

    yaydr (yet another yafaray distributed raytracer) is (or: will be) a fully
distributed and decentralised frontend for network rendering yafaray xml files,
focussed on video rendering.

--------

-Have fun rendering your stuff! Will be upping to Archlinux AUR
-Compiling: (I'll create standard makefile later on)
 *install code::blocks
 *open project file
 *click build and run
 *enjoy!

run
g++ -oyaydr -Iinclude/ -lz -lfreetype -lyafaraycore -DHAVE_PTHREAD -lboost_thread -lboost_system -lboost_random -lboost_filesystem -lcryptopp -lpthread main.cpp src/*
to compile.

Report bugs on github -> Issues.
